it is by default a type= text type.

21
00:01:13.118 --> 00:01:15.154
And then I threw a bunch of other
ones on there just for use.

22
00:01:15.154 --> 00:01:16.824
So you can have a color selector.

23
00:01:16.824 --> 00:01:22.238
So let's say we wanna choose a nice,
I don't know, a green, okay?

24
00:01:22.238 --> 00:01:26.050
So someone could do that, right?

25
00:01:26.050 --> 00:01:28.335
And now, they've selected a green color,

26
00:01:28.335 --> 00:01:32.485
maybe you have them choosing the color
of the t-shirt that they're creating.

27
00:01:32.485 --> 00:01:35.641
This is a file selector.

28
00:01:35.641 --> 00:01:40.367
So I can upload a file or something like
that, I can go select this file here and

29
00:01:40.367 --> 00:01:43.524
this will upload this file or
something like that.

