which file that they wanna select.

32
00:01:49.263 --> 00:01:52.194
This is a number, right?

33
00:01:52.194 --> 00:01:57.135
So I can only enter,
only numbers will be allowed here.

34
00:01:57.135 --> 00:02:03.058
And then I can put numbers here, and
they'll have the down arrow and up arrow.

35
00:02:03.058 --> 00:02:05.727
That's a number selector.

36
00:02:05.727 --> 00:02:12.059
This one is for users, if they need
to select a time and date, all right?

37
00:02:12.059 --> 00:02:16.539
So for this one,
they wanted to do May 1, 2022.

38
00:02:16.539 --> 00:02:21.684
This will allow them to do that,
and then this will allow

39
00:02:21.684 --> 00:02:26.507
them to select a time as
like 12:30 AM on May 1.

