00:02:26.507 --> 00:02:29.751
Radio buttons, so
if you have five options and

41
00:02:29.751 --> 00:02:34.340
you wanna user to choose one of them,
you'll use radio buttons.

42
00:02:34.340 --> 00:02:38.925
