00:02:38.925 --> 00:02:42.089
then you'll use checkboxes, right?

44
00:02:42.089 --> 00:02:43.943
And that's what those are.

45
00:02:45.011 --> 00:02:50.168
So I think that's most of the types there,
there might be a couple more, but

46
00:02:50.168 --> 00:02:55.569
I don't know, I don't use the color
selector very option because typically,

47
00:02:55.569 --> 00:02:58.574
I don't need users to select colors for
me.

48
00:02:58.574 --> 00:03:01.150
But if I did, that's what that's for.

